milestones.description: Steven Taylor and Modani's 107-run partnership is USA's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 52 between Alexander and Mark Johnson
Steven Taylor has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (7) in ODIs for USA, going past Hutchinson's 4
Assad Vala has scored 4 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for PNG breaking Vani Morea's record
Steven Taylor has broken the record for most sixes (10) in ODIs for USA, going past Aaron Jones's 6
Steven Taylor has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (70) in an innings in ODIs for USA, going past Aaron Jones's 44
Netravalkar has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (14) for USA, going past Aaron Jones
